OL,3,CMoment Met Police officer, cleared of
OL,4,Cgross misconduct, fires Taser at
OL,5,Cgirl, ten
OL,7,FVideo footage shows the moment a
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police officer fired his
OL,9,FTaser at a ten-year-old girl
OL,10,Fbrandishing a pair of garden sheers.
OL,12,FThe video was released by the IOPC
OL,13,Fpolice watchdog, which at a
OL,14,Fdisciplinary hearing on Thursday
OL,15,Fcleared PC Jonathan Broadhead of
OL,16,Fgross misconduct.
OL,18,FIt shows the officer firing his Taser
OL,19,Ftwice at the girl within seconds of
OL,20,Fentering her home in south-west
OL,21,FLondon on January 21, 2021.
